    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You probably don't have the <code>INTERNET</code> permission. Try adding this to your <code>AndroidManifest.xml</code> file, right before <code>&lt;/manifest&gt;</code>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;uses-permission android:name=\"android.permission.INTERNET\" /&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><sup>Note: the above doesn't <em>have to be</em> right before the <code>&lt;/manifest&gt;</code> tag, but that is a good / correct place to put it.</sup></p>\n\n<p><sup>Note: if this answer doesn't help in your case, read the other answers!</sup></p>\n"
