    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Sometimes, although you add <code>&lt;uses-permission android:name=\"android.permission.INTERNET\" /&gt;</code> in the AndroidManifest and you have a WiFi connection, this exception can be thrown. In my case, I have turned off WiFi and then turned it on again. This resolved the error. Weird solution, but sometimes it works.</p>\n"
