    "creation_date" : 1481614650,
    "answer_id" : 41115789,
    "question_id" : 6355498,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I Had the same problem, and it was because the simulator somehow got in airplane mode, once this was disabled my App worked fine :-)\nI had tried everything, rebuild, clean+build and reboot android studio and reboot the computer, even reinstalling android studio..</p>\n"
